From cou.: 6 All analyses were performed on an Optimass 8000 (GBC Scientific Equipment Pty. Ltd., Australia) ICP-MS system, which is an orthogonally accelerated time-of-flight (oa-TOF) mass spectrometer coupled with an ICP torch. Samples were introduced by a modified Varian GTA-95, which was described previously.6 The samples consisted of 10 μL aliquots of 10 ppb multi-metal solution, performed in quadruplicate.
From Soup: 6 All analyses were performed on an Optimass 8000 (GBC Scientific Equipment Pty. Ltd., Australia) ICP-MS system, which is an orthogonally accelerated time-of-flight (oa-TOF) mass spectrometer coupled with an ICP torch. Samples were introduced by a modified Varian GTA-95, which was described previously. 6 The samples consisted of 10 μL aliquots of 10 ppb multi-metal solution, performed in quadruplicate.
