From Soup: 37 Many metal halides and a few metal oxides can produce reasonable vapor pressures at ambient temperatures, and a list of possibilities was generated and their vapor pressures determined. From a list of ca. 100 candidates, NbF 5 , TiBr 4 and SnBr 4 were isolated and then experimentally evaluated by placing a small amount of the salt into a stainless steel column between plugs of glass wool.
