From Soup: 50 Other species were available ( i.e. 19 F + and 47 SiF + ) but were not used since three masses were already present in the low range. The 19 F + and 47 SiF + both behaved similarly to 28 Si + in respect to changes in lens potentials. When the skimmer and extraction were adjusted, 19 F + had a similar behavior to 79 Br + ( e.g. increasing or decreasing at an exaggerated rate) including the Z lens behavior.
