From cou.: 53 e.g.
From Soup: 53 While the calibrator discussed in this paper used an array of materials to achieve a range of masses to monitor, a simpler device could also be constructed. For example, a simple device with two parallel lines of 1/4″ Tygon® tubing with simple valves could be constructed. SnBr 4 could be placed between plugs of glass wool in one line and the other line used as a bypass line to adjust the total gas flow to the ICP.
